Help

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


This is a maintenance category, used for maintenance of the Wikipedia project. It is not part of the encyclopedia and contains non-article pages, or groups articles by status rather than subject. Do not include this category in content categories.
Pages in this category should be moved to subcategories where applicable. This category may require frequent maintenance to avoid becoming too large. It should directly contain very few, if any, pages and should mainly contain subcategories.
This is a meta-category for organizing WikiProjects according to subject area or task.
You should place your WikiProject's main page and/or main WikiProject category in one of the sub-categories of this category, not directly in this category. Some of the sub-categories (such as Science WikiProjects) are further subdivided.  Please note that the category for Wikipedia WikiProjects is for WikiProjects dealing with some aspect of Wikipedia maintenance (such as spam-fighting or copyediting), rather than a WikiProject dealing with a particular content area (such as history or biographies).
